getPlantById.display-name: Get plant by ID (OAuth OR OrgApiKeyAuth)

__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  OauthScope:
    enum:
      - value: read:plants
        name: ReadPlants
        docs: Read access to plant information
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  GetPlantByIdResponse:
    properties:
      id: optional<integer>
      name: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    getPlantById:
      path: /plants/{plantId}
      method: GET
      auth:
        - OAuth:
            - read:plants
        - OrgApiKeyAuth: []
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      path-parameters:
        plantId: integer
      display-name: Get plant by ID (OAuth OR OrgApiKeyAuth)
      response:
        docs: Plant details
        type: GetPlantByIdResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - path-parameters:
            plantId: 1
          headers:
            x-api-key: '[object Object]'
            x-org-api-key: '[object Object]'
          response:
            body:
              id: 1
              name: name
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Security Multiple Options Test
environments:
  Default: https://api.example.com/v1
default-environment: Default
auth-schemes:
  BearerAuthScheme:
    scheme: bearer
auth: BearerAuthScheme
headers:
  x-api-key:
    type: string
    name: apiKey
  x-org-api-key:
    type: string
    name: orgApiKey
